    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute showroom condition, meticulously maintained and preserved to the highest standard. The exterior features a flawless factory finish with no imperfections, while the interior remains in pristine, like-new condition with all original features functioning perfectly. Mechanical performance is exceptional, reflecting a complete service history and careful ownership. Potential buyers can expect a vehicle that looks and drives as if it just left the dealership floor.",
