    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the legendary S54 naturally aspirated inline-six. This unit exhibits crisp throttle response via its individual throttle bodies and remains mechanically stout with the critical rod bearing service recently completed. The Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise gate engagement, paired with a rear subframe that has been proactively reinforced to handle the torque loads. Suspension geometry remains true, utilizing refreshed bushings for optimal lateral grip. While showing honest patina consistent with its mileage, the chassis rigidity and VANOS timing system are in excellent working order, making this a turn-key performance machine for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
