      "description": "This meticulously maintained sedan offers a premium driving experience at an excellent value. The exterior presents beautifully with a high-gloss finish, though it shows a few minor, age-appropriate stone chips on the front fascia. Inside, the smoke-free cabin is remarkably clean; the leather upholstery is supple and free of tears, showing only light softening on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All power features, including the sunroof and infotainment system, operate flawlessly. Under the hood, the vehicle has been serviced strictly according to the manufacturer's schedule, resulting in a smooth, responsive engine and tight handling. It recently passed a full safety inspection and comes with a complete set of service records. This is a reliable, turn-key vehicle perfect for anyone seeking quality and longevity.",
